values:
today is my sister's graduation from high school. this is my second yougest sister who is graduating and boy, does it make me feel old.  doesn't help that there is 9 years between me and the first younger sister.  or that there is 21 years between me and my younger brother!  
ok, new meds seem to be working out okay.  happy about that, but mood swings are still pretty bad.  find myself yelling a lot.  i guess that's to be worked through.  looking for a new job because this one is going south fast.

anyhoo, update on my last entries' to-do list:
-i sent out my returns and am expecting some cashback soon; 
-sent out the baby onesie to my expectant friend; 
-worked more on my daughter's ponch; 
-i designed come toe rings that turned out cool, new anklet design, too; 
-organized closed from winter to summer; 
-got a hair cut; 
-shaved hubby's head

